                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc form="codex">
                            <supportDesc material="perg">
                                <support>
                                    <p>
                                        <material>Parchment</material>.</p>
                                </support>
                                <extent>2 leaves. Fol. 1 measures <dimensions scope="range"
                                        type="leaf">
                                        <height unit="mm">268-272</height>
                                        <width unit="mm">185-193</width>
                                    </dimensions>, fol. 2 measures <dimensions scope="range"
                                        type="leaf">
                                        <height unit="mm">265-269</height>
                                        <width unit="mm">193</width>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </extent>
                                <collation>The two leaves are conjoint.</collation>
                                <condition>The outer margin and the outer corners are excised but
                                        with no loss of text except from the five top lines of the
                                        outer columns of fol. 1 (partly crumbled away) of which 9 mm
                                        of the lines are missing. A third of the lines of the outer
                                        columns of fol. 2 are also missing. It appears as if there
                                        are stitching holes along the spine.</condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout columns="2" writtenLines="40">
                                    <p>The leaves are written in two columns with 40 lines per
                                        column, the size of the columns are approx. <dimensions
                                            scope="all" type="written">
                                            <height unit="mm">218</height>
                                            <width unit="mm">75-80</width>
                                        </dimensions>. Spaces on 3 lines are left empty for
                                        majuscules, except from a Þ containing a face on f. 2rb that
                                        later has been drawn in.</p>
                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
